  <ion-view hide-nav-bar="true" >
  <div class="bar bar-header bar-color ">
  <a href="#/tab/trial" style="color:#ffffff;" class="button icon ion-ios-arrow-back button-clear head_button1">返回</a>
  <h1 class="title">试用详情</h1>
<!--   <button style="color:#ffffff;" class="button  icon ion-ios-redo button-clear" ng-click="fenxiang()">分享</button> -->
  </div>
  <ion-content class="padding_head">
  <div ng-if="sy_showloading" style="margin-top:60px; text-align: center">
    <ion-spinner icon="ios" style="height: 60px; width: 60px;;"></ion-spinner>
  </div>

    <div class="ibody" ng-show="sy_showloading ==false" >
      <div class="i_tryout">
        <div class="s_part2">
          <div class="hang1">
            <img ng-if="showdata.thumb"   ng-src="{{ showdata.thumb | imgUrl }}" />
          </div>
          <div class="hang2">
            <div class="L">{{showdata.title | limitTo:18 }}</div>
            <div ng-show = "showdata.protype == 2" class="R">送图片商品</div>
            <div     class="R2">包邮</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="s_part3">
          <div class="hang1 c5">
            {{showdata.price_name}}
            <span>{{showdata.goods_price | currency:"￥"  }}</span> <i ng-show = "showdata.protype == 3 ">(赠
              <span>{{showdata.goods_bonus }}</span>
              元红包)</i> 
          </div>
          <div class="hang2">
          <span class="a1">  <span class="c4">限量份数：</span><span class="c5">{{showdata.goods_number}}份</span></span>
            <span class="a2"><span class="c4">剩余份数：</span><span class="c5">{{showdata.number}}份</span></span>
            <span class="a1"><span class="c4">申请人数：</span><span class="c5">{{showdata.apply_people}}人</span></span>
            <span class="a2">
              <span class="c4">剩余时间：</span><span class="c5"> <i id="{{showdata.end_time}}"  >{{showdata.end_time  | f_fomtime  }}</i></span>
            </span>
            <div class="clearfix"></div>
          </div>
          <!--hang2-->
          <div class="hang3 c5">
              <img ng-src="img/a3.jpg"  /> 商家已存保证金<b class="cc" >{{ showdata.goods_deposit | currency:"￥" }}</b>请放心申请
          </div>
          <!--hang3-->
                   <div class="hang4">
            <div class="ti">试用流程</div>
            <div class="co c4">
              1、申请试用，获得试用资格
              <br>
              2、按照提示以 <b class="cc">{{showdata.goods_price | currency:"￥"  }}</b>
              去指定平台购物
              <br>
              3、回平台填写购买付款的订单号
              <br>
              4、确认收货-给予评价-填写试用报告
              <br>
              5、系统返还
              <b class="cc">{{ (showdata.goods_bonus -1 +1 )  +  (showdata.goods_price -1 +1 ) | currency:"￥"  }}</b> 
              到您平台账户中
              <br></div>
          </div>
          <!--hang4-->
          <div class="hang4">
            <div class="ti">注意事项</div>
            <div class="co c4">
              1.与商家聊天的时候不要提及试用相关信息。
              <br>
              2.禁止通过淘宝客.返利网等返现网站链接下单。
              <br>
              3.不要催促商家发货.返款,请遵守平台相关规定。
              <br></div>
          </div>
          <!--hang4-->
          <div class="hang5">
            <div class="ti">温馨提示</div>
            <div class="co c4">
              1.完善个人相关资料，可以提高通过率。
              <br>
              2.分享活动链接至QQ好友,微信朋友圈,微信好友,邀请他们参与有奖励。
              <br>
              3.在申请理由里面详细的介绍一下个人的试用经历和心得,更有助提高通过率。
              <br></div>
          </div>
          <!--hang5 搜索下单流程图-->
          
          <div class="hang6">
            <img ng-src="img/sosuo.png"    ng-show="showdata.type == 'search'  "    >
            <img ng-src="img/saoma.png"  ng-show=" showdata.type == 'qrcode' "   >
            <img ng-src="img/ak.png"  ng-show=" showdata.type == 'ask'   "    >
          </div>
        </div>
        <!--s_part3-->
        <div class="s_part6 c5">
          <div class="part sel" ng-click="goods_body()" >活动详情</div>
          <div class="part" ng-click="good_user_list()" >已申请({{showdata.apply_people}})</div>
          <div class="part" ng-click="report_lists()">试用报告({{showdata.finish_people}})</div>
          <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </div>
        <!--s_part6-->
        <div class="s_part7 ccc" ng-show= "Switch == 1 "   style="display:">

          <div ng-bind-html="showdata.goods_content | f_img_url  " ></div>

        </div>

        <!--s_part7-->
        <div class="s_part8" ng-show= "Switch == 2 "  >

          <div ng-if="user_list_showloading" style="margin-top:60px; text-align: center">
            <ion-spinner icon="ios" style="height: 60px; width: 60px;;"></ion-spinner>
          </div>

          <div class="list" style="display:" ng-show = "  user_list_showloading == false && user_list != '' "    >

            <a class="part" href="#" ng-repeat="d in user_list" >
              <div class="hang1" >
                <img ng-src="{{ ENV.imgUrl +  d.avatar  }}" ></div>
              <!--hang1-->
              <div class="hang2 c4">{{d.nickname | f_nickname | limitTo : 5 }}</div>
            </a>

            <div class="clearfix"></div>
          </div>
          <!--s_list-->

          <div class="tis c4" style="display:" ng-show = "user_list_showloading == false && user_list == '' "   >暂时还没有人申请</div>
        </div>
        <!--s_part8-->
        <div class="s_part9"  ng-show= "Switch == 3 " >
          <div ng-if="report_list_showloading" style="margin-top:60px; text-align: center">
            <ion-spinner icon="ios" style="height: 60px; width: 60px;;"></ion-spinner>
          </div>

          <div class="no c4" style="display:"  ng-show="report_list_showloading==false && report_list == ''  "   >新品上架,暂时还未有人完成试用报告！</div>
          <div ng-show="report_list_showloading==false && report_list != ''  ">
          <div class="list" ng-repeat="d in report_list"  >
            <div class="hang ">
              <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                <tr>
                  <td class="L c5">
                    <div class="co">
                      <img  ng-src="{{ ENV.imgUrl +  d.avatar}}"></div>
                      <div>{{d.nickname | f_nickname }}</div>
                   </td>
                  <td class="R">
                    <div class="a1 c4">
                      <div  ng-bind-html="d.content | f_report_img_url"></div>
                      <img ng-if="d.thumb  != ''"   ng-src="{{d.thumb | imgUrl  }}"></div>
                    <div class="a2 c4">提交时间:{{d.inputtime + '000'  | date:"yyyy/MM/dd h:mm" }}</div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>

            <!--hang--> </div>
            <ion-infinite-scroll
                          pulling-text="加载更多中"
                          on-infinite="sybg_loadMore()"
                          ng-if="sybg_hasNextPage"
                          distance="1%">
            </ion-infinite-scroll>
          </div>
          <!--list--> </div>
        <!--s_part9--> </div>
      <!--i_tryout--> </div>
    </div>
  </ion-content>

  <script id="a.html" type="text/ng-template"> 
          <ion-item ng-show="bind_phone == 1 && phone_status == 1 " class="item item-icon-left item-icon-right ">
              <i class="icon ion-checkmark-circled" style="font-size:18px;color:green" ></i>
              手机认证
              <i class="item-note">已认证</i>
          </ion-item>

          <ion-item ng-show="bind_phone == 1   && phone_status != 1"  class="item item-icon-left item-icon-right " href="#/tab/user/profile/phone"  >
              <i class=" icon ion-close-circled"   style="font-size:18px;color:red"></i>
              手机认证
              <i class="item-note">未认证</i>
              <i class="icon ion-ios-arrow-right" style="font-size:18px;color:#666"></i>
          </ion-item>

          <ion-item  ng-show="bind_email ==2 && emall_status ==1 " class="item item-icon-left item-icon-right ">
           <i class="icon ion-checkmark-circled" style="font-size:18px;color:green" ></i>
              邮箱认证
              <i class="item-note">已认证</i>
          </ion-item>

          <ion-item ng-show="bind_email == 2   && emall_status != 1 "  class="item item-icon-left item-icon-right " href="#/tab/user/profile/email" >
              <i class=" icon ion-close-circled"   style="font-size:18px;color:red"></i>
              邮箱认证
              <i class="item-note">未认证</i>
              <i class="icon ion-ios-arrow-right" style="font-size:18px;color:#666"></i>
          </ion-item>


          <ion-item  ng-show="realname ==3 && name_status ==1 " class="item item-icon-left item-icon-right ">
           <i class="icon ion-checkmark-circled" style="font-size:18px;color:green" ></i>
              实名认证
              <i class="item-note">已认证</i>
          </ion-item>


          <ion-item ng-show="realname == 3 && name_status == -1 "  class="item item-icon-left item-icon-right " href="#/tab/user/profile/card" >
              <i class=" icon ion-close-circled"   style="font-size:18px;color:red"></i>
              实名认证
              <i class="item-note">{{name_status | f_name_status }}</i>
              <i class="icon ion-ios-arrow-right" style="font-size:18px;color:#666"></i>
          </ion-item>

          <ion-item ng-show="realname == 3 && name_status == '' "  class="item item-icon-left item-icon-right " href="#/tab/user/profile/card" >
              <i class=" icon ion-close-circled"   style="font-size:18px;color:red"></i>
              实名认证
              <i class="item-note">{{name_status | f_name_status }}</i>
              <i class="icon ion-ios-arrow-right" style="font-size:18px;color:#666"></i>
          </ion-item>

          <ion-item ng-show="realname == 3 && name_status == null "  class="item item-icon-left item-icon-right " href="#/tab/user/profile/card" >
              <i class=" icon ion-close-circled"   style="font-size:18px;color:red"></i>
              实名认证
              <i class="item-note">{{name_status | f_name_status }}</i>
              <i class="icon ion-ios-arrow-right" style="font-size:18px;color:#666"></i>
          </ion-item>


          <ion-item ng-show="realname == 3 && name_status == 0 "  class="item item-icon-left item-icon-right " >
              <i class=" icon ion-close-circled"   style="font-size:18px;color:red"></i>
              实名认证
              <i class="item-note">{{name_status | f_name_status }}</i>
          </ion-item>

          <ion-item  ng-show="bind_alipay ==5 && allpay_status ==1 " class="item item-icon-left item-icon-right ">
           <i class="icon ion-checkmark-circled" style="font-size:18px;color:green" ></i>
              支付宝
              <i class="item-note">已绑定</i>
          </ion-item>


          <ion-item ng-show=" bind_alipay ==5 && allpay_status !=1 "  class="item item-icon-left item-icon-right " href="#/tab/user/profile/alipay" >
              <i class=" icon ion-close-circled"   style="font-size:18px;color:red"></i>
              支付宝
              <i class="item-note">未绑定</i>
              <i class="icon ion-ios-arrow-right" style="font-size:18px;color:#666"></i>
          </ion-item>

          <ion-item ng-show=" bind_taobao == 4 && data_bind_taobao.count > 0 "  class="item item-icon-left item-icon-right " >
              <i class="icon ion-checkmark-circled" style="font-size:18px;color:green" ></i>
              淘宝帐号
              <i class="item-note">已绑{{data_bind_taobao.count}}个</i>
          </ion-item>
          
          <ion-item ng-show=" bind_taobao == 4 && data_bind_taobao.count < 1 "  class="item item-icon-left item-icon-right " href="#/tab/user/profile/taobao"    >
              <i class=" icon ion-close-circled"   style="font-size:18px;color:red"></i>
              淘宝帐号
              <i class="item-note">未绑定</i>
              <i class="icon ion-ios-arrow-right" style="font-size:18px;color:#666"></i>
          </ion-item>
  </script>
  <script id="b.html" type="text/ng-template"> 

                <label ng-if=' bind_taobao == 4' class="item item-input item-select  "  style="height:50px">
                  <select ng-model="vm.data_bind_taobao_default.id" ng-options="a.id as a.account for a  in data_bind_taobao.lists">
                  </select>
                </label>

                  <p  ng-if=' bind_taobao == 4' style="color:#A9A9A9" class="padding-left">请使用选定淘宝帐号下单</p>
                  <label ng-if=' reason == 7 ' class="item item-input" >
                    <textarea  ng-model="vm.Application_reasons"  placeholder="对商家说点什么,提高通过率" rows="4"></textarea>
                  </label>                
                  <p style="color:#A9A9A9" class="padding-left">未按要求下单,可能会被取消资格!</p>

  </script>
  <script id="c.html" type="text/ng-template">              
                  <ion-item class="height60" >{{showdata.goods_rule.ask.question}}</ion-item>
                  <label class="item item-input" >                 
                    <input type="text"  ng-model="vm.Answer" placeholder="请输入答案" ></label>


                   <h5 style="color:#A9A9A9" class="padding-left">温馨提示: {{vm.Answer}}</h5>
                   <p style="color:#A9A9A9" class="padding-left">1.{{showdata.goods_rule.ask.tips}}</p>
                   <p style="color:#A9A9A9" class="padding-left">2.<a href="{{showdata.goods_url}}">点击去宝贝页面找答案</a></p>
  </script>

  <script id="e.html" type="text/ng-template">              
                <label class="item item-input item-select  " style="height:50px">
                  <select ng-model="vm.data_bind_taobao_default.id" ng-options="a.id as a.account for a  in data_bind_taobao.lists">
                  </select>
                </label>

                  <p  ng-if='bind_taobao == 4' style="color:#A9A9A9" class="padding-left">请使用选定淘宝帐号下单</p>
  </script>
<div class="i_tryout_s_part4" ng-if= "login_status == 0"  >
    <a ng-click="Apply_trial()" class="a1">免费申请</a>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>

<div class="i_tryout_s_part4" ng-if= "order_is_join.data == 1 && showdata.number > 0 "  >
    <a ng-click="Apply_trial()" class="a1">免费申请</a>
    <a ng-click="vip_Apply_trial()" ng-show =" showdata.goods_vipfree == 1">vip快速试用</a>
    <a ng-click="jinbi_Apply_trial()" ng-show =" showdata.goods_point > 0" >{{showdata.point_num}}积分兑换</a>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>

  <!--s_part4-->
<div class="i_tryout_s_part4"  ng-if= "order_is_join.data == 0 &&  showdata.end_time > data_time "  >
  <a href="#" class="a1" style="background:#ccc; color:#FFF; border:0px ">已申请过</a>
  <a href="#/tab/user/trial_order" >查看我的订单</a>
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>

<div class="i_tryout_s_part4"  ng-if= " order_is_join.data == 1 && showdata.end_time < data_time "  >
  <a class="a1" style="background:#ccc; color:#FFF; border:0px ">活动结束</a>
  当前活动时间已结束,下次早点来呃。
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>

<div class="i_tryout_s_part4"  ng-if= " showdata.number < 1 "  >
  <a class="a1" style="background:#ccc; color:#FFF; border:0px ">木有了 下次早点来</a>
   留意后续是否有追加。
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>

<!--s_part4-->


</ion-view>